This application works only in  linux



==============INSTRUCTIONS=================


1) For running GUI : python test2.py
2) Recording is saved in demo.wav
3) Recording is done till the voice goes down by certain threshold
4) After playing the song you need to press it again to completely kill the process
5) fork has been used. So multiple processes can run at at time
6) Temporary files are used in which the changed files are stored.Their names are temp0.wav,temp1.wavtemp2.wavtemp3.wavtemp4.wav







